# Project

Next.js **16** · React **19** · Sanity **v6** · Tailwind **v4** · RTL Urdu · https://darulquran.pk

```bash
npm run dev      # :3001, /studio
npm run build    # prebuild stubs polyfills
npm run lint && npm run check:urdu
```

Env (never commit): `NEXT_PUBLIC_SANITY_*`, `SANITY_API_TOKEN`, `EMAIL_*`, `NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL`

- CMS content only — no hardcoded contacts/nav
- `safeFetch` → Sanity; `revalidate = 300` on CMS routes
- Brand: `dq-*`; font: `DeferredUrduFont`
